title: Welcome To My Blog
text:
This is the first post in a Quarto blog. Welcome!

Since this post doesn’t specify an explicit image, the first image in the post will be used in the listing page of posts.

title: About
text: I’m a physicist by training, but a Data Scientist by practice. I’ve been coding things in R and Python for about 15 years, and I finally decided that I wanted a place to put my fun projects. I also wanted to figure out how Quarto works. So this is a place for me to do that. Plus, I thought it would be fun to just play with some data. And I just learned about #TidyTuesday and the Data Science Learning Community.
